    <a href="home.html#services">Services</a>
    <a href="home.html#about">About</a>
    <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Design & Branding</h1>
  <p>We design modern data-driven interfaces and powerful brand identities for digital and analytics-focused businesses.</p>
</section>

<div class="container">

  <h3>What We Offer</h3>

  <div class="grid">

    <div class="card">
      <h4>📊 Dashboard UI Design</h4>
      <p>Clean, modern dashboards for analytics platforms, Power BI, and data systems.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>🎨 Brand Identity</h4>
      <p>Professional logos, color systems, and visual identity tailored for tech companies.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>📈 Data Visualisation Design</h4>
      <p>Custom charts, reports, and data visuals that communicate insights clearly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>💼 Corporate Branding</h4>
      <p>Business profiles, pitch decks, and corporate documents for enterprise clients.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>🧠 UX/UI Strategy</h4>
      <p>User-focused design to improve usability and engagement across platforms.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h4>🚀 Digital Product Design</h4>
      <p>Design for SaaS platforms, apps, and data-driven systems.</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <h3>Why Choose Trafsol?</h3>
  <p>
  At Trafsol Data Specialists, we combine data expertise with modern design to create powerful digital experiences. 
  Our designs are not just visually appealing — they are built to improve usability, drive engagement, and support business growth.
  </p>

  <a href="pricing.html" class="cta">View Pricing</a>

</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 Trafsol Data Specialists
</footer>

</body>
</html>
